            <section id="section1">
                <h1 id="art_h1">Cyber Security</h1>
        
                <p id="art_p">
                Cyber security means the practice of defending computers, servers, mobile devices, electronic systems, networks, and data from malicious attacks. It is also known as IT security or electronic information security.
                The term applies in a variety of contexts, from business to mobile computing, and can be broken down into a few common categories.
                Network security is the practice of securing a computer network from hackers, whether they are targeted attackers or opportunistic malware.
                </p> 
       
            </section>

        
