            <section id="section9">
                <h1 id="art_h1">Cyber Security Challenges</h1>
                <p id="art_p">To achieve effective cybersecurity, an organization needs to coordinate its efforts throughout its information system. Its components include all of the following:</p>
                <ul id="art_ul">
                    <li id="art_li">Network Security</li>
                    <li id="art_li">Application Security</li>
                    <li id="art_li">Data Security</li>
                    <li id="art_li">Identity Management</li>
                    <li id="art_li">Database and Infrastructure Security</li>
                    <li id="art_li">Phone Protection</li>
                    <li id="art_li">Disaster Recovery / Business Continuity Planning</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
        
